  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 7th, your conviction is unbreakable and has become a rock for your allies to rely on. Twice per rest, when you or an ally within 30 feet of you would make a saving throw against mental condition, you may spend one EX Die and add +1d4 to the roll.</p><p>Additionally, when you are above 50% HP, you are immune to charmed, berserk, and frightened conditions. Additionally, you cannot be forced to directly work against your Goal, Ambition, or Drive. When you fall below 50% this becomes advantage against saves and checks against these effects.</p>",
